lead_paragraph: Middlesbrough maintained its unbeaten start to life back in the English Premier League by drawing 0-0 with West Bromwich Albion in a match of few clear-cut opportunities at The Hawthorns on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Middlesbrough Stays Unbeaten After 0-0 Draw at West Brom
